name: Traveler (Geo)
description: A traveler from another world who had their only kin taken away, forcing them to embark on a journey to find The Seven.

skills.name: Normal Attack: Foreign Rockblade
skills.description: Normal AttackPerforms up to 5 rapid strikes.Charged AttackConsumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.Plunging AttackPlunges from mid-air to strike the ground below, damaging opponents along the path and dealing AoE DMG upon impact.

skills.name: Starfell Sword
skills.description: You disgorge a meteorite from the depths of the earth, dealing AoE Geo DMG.The meteorite is considered a Geo Construct, and can be climbed or used to block attacks.HoldThis skill's positioning may be adjusted.
skills.info: You spoke with Paimon about the final destination of falling stars.

skills.name: Wake of Earth
skills.description: Energizing the Geo deep underground, you set off expanding shockwaves.Launches surrounding opponents back and deals AoE Geo DMG.A stone wall is erected at the edges of the shockwave.The stone wall is considered a Geo Construct, and may be used to block attacks.
skills.info: You and Paimon studied the pulse of the mountains.
